### Registro PUBLICO de usuarios
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Francisquito",
	"email": "francisco@gmail.com",
	"password": "12345678"
}
### Auth User

POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "identifier": "francisco@gmail.com",
	"password": "12345678"
}

### Obtener intereses del usuario por su ID de usuario

GET http://localhost:4000/api/users/1/interests